## ğŸ—ï¸ Development

If you want to modify or contribute to the app:

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/al1kss/pizza-app.git
   cd pizza-app
   ```

2. Install in development mode:
   ```bash
   pip install -e .
   ```

3. Make your changes and test:
   ```bash
   pizza-app
   ```

